# 4. System Architecture

## High-Level Architecture

```text
Medical PDFs
      ↓
PDF Extraction
      ↓
Chunking
      ↓
Embeddings
      ↓
ChromaDB Vector Storage
      ↓
Entity Extraction
      ↓
Neo4j Knowledge Graph
      ↓
Hybrid Retrieval
      ↓
Reranking
      ↓
Context Building
      ↓
Generator LLM
      ↓
Evaluator LLM
      ↓
Confidence Scoring
      ↓
Final API Response
```

